asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: David Attenborough
description: FLUF world alternate reality David Attenborough was created during a critical period of Sir David Attenboroughs life. In 1947, while studying zoology at Clare College in Cambridge, Sir David Attenborough was called up for national service in the her majestys Royal Navy. The Sir David Attenborough who went on to produce world renown natural world documentaries complied and served in North Wales for two years. FLUF world David Attenborough wanted nothing to do with the military and promptly hopped off to Italy. Attempting to blend into his new surroundings, David started learning more about Italian culture. As a quick study, he quickly became an expect in the underground subculture of Italian Sports Cars. He was enthralled by the fast lifestyle and the passion he saw and soon started producing documentaries. By the end of the 1950s, David Attenboroughs films of sports cars were massively popular with one notable fan being the young Ferruccio Lamborghini. Ferruccio and David hit it off straight away and immediately started developing prototypes of their vision for the next generation of sport car that would push the boundaries of style and function. In 1963, Ferruccio and David launched their new Italian Sport Car company named Lamborghini as David couldnt be associated with the branding as he was still wanted for dodging his military service with the Royal Navy. Together with Ferruccios manufacturing expertise and Davids ground breaking designs, Automobili Lamborghini S.p.A. would go on to become a leader in innovation. Davids designs were a lightning bolt to the entire industry and a cult like devotion amongst its followers as LamboGang was born. To this day, David Attenboroughs influence in sports car design is unmistakable. From his earlier drawings which would become the Miura sports coupe to his guiding hand that brought the world the Countach. Receiver of all of the awards, David is heralded as the finest sports car designer the world has even seen. Still holding the role of lead design advisor, David is mostly retired and enjoys spending time in the underground typing LamboGang in Discord Chat Rooms as fast as he can for long uninterrupted periods to show his support for his followers. David can be seen here in a photo taken during the his early years proudly showing off his well developed physic, his stylish gold chain, and the first car he owned. LamboGang

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---
